PYTHON +3.14

Install pip packages:

-m pip install numpy pandas yfinance pyyaml


Pick a date within the powershell YYYY-MM-DD

Run Fast Model:
.\.venv\Scripts\python.exe -m scurve.run --asof YYYY-MM-DD --config .\SCurve\config\scurve_config_fast.yaml



Run the normal model: Select date-
\.venv\Scripts\python.exe SCurve\scurve\run.py --asof YYYY-MM-DD --config SCurve\config\scurve_config.yaml

or

python -m scurve.run --asof YYYY-MM-DD --config SCurve\config\scurve_config.yaml


In powershell:
Example:
--asof 2026-03-03 --config SCurve\config\scurve_config.yaml

python -m scurve.run --asof 2026-03-10 --config SCurve\config\scurve_config.yaml


Output csv files will appear in a run/YYYYMMDD folder inside of the scurve/data/raw folder.

Example:

/scurve/data/run/20260303/
    fit_diagnostics.csv
    portfolio_weights.csv
    scores.csv
